    <div class="documentTop">
      <h1>Press centre</h1>
      
      <p>Welcome to the press centre of the Ministry og Fisheries and Coastal Affairs.</p>
<p><strong>The Ministry of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs is exclusively using the telephone number +47 22 24 66 99 &nbsp;as the media contact line between 08&nbsp;and 15.45 o'clock on weekdays. From 15 May till 15 September the opening hours are between 8 and 15.00 o'clock.</strong></p>
<p>The Communication Unit relays press enquiries to the political leadership. We help the press and the public to find background materials and information on ministerial matters. We are also responsible for the Ministry’s website. Through the press service we wish to do the best job possible to enable journalists and the public to quickly find information relating to our areas of responsibility and receive answers to their questions.</p>
<p>The communication policy of the Ministry of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs is based on the main principles of the Freedom of Information Act and the Public Administration Act, which give the public the right of access to our work and our decisions. We attach importance to being open and accessible and providing good service to the media and others who contact us with enquiries. We are set up to pursue an active communication policy and require that the information we provide be correct, objective and reliable.</p>
<p>The most important matters being dealt with by the Ministry at any given time will be presented on the Ministry’s home page. News regarding special topics will also be published on special topics pages. </p>
<p>The Ministry is connected to an electronic mail journal, a project run by Statskonsult, which gives over 80 editorial offices access to the Ministry’s public journal. Editorial offices require a user ID and password, which are administered by Statskonsult. </p>
<p><strong>The Ministry of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs sends out press releases by e-mail. If you wish to receive press releases from us, you can let us know here (News alerts by e-mail)</strong></p>
<ul>
