<li><a href="/en/dep/fkd/Press-Centre/Picture-Archive.html?id=286">Press photo of the political leadership</a></li>
<li><a href="/en/dep/fkd/The-Ministry-of-Fisheries-and-Coastal-Affairs/Senior-administrative-staff.html?id=280">Administrative leadership</a> </li></ul>      
